name: Goku I
description:
New progress has been made in dark matter detection. On November 29, London time, "Nature" published online research results of Chinese scientists: using the "Wukong" satellite to obtain the world's most accurate high-energy electron cosmic ray energy spectrum, it will be determined that the energy is less than 1TeV (electron cosmic ray (1TeV=1 Whether the trillion electron volts comes from dark matter plays a key role and may provide new evidence for the existence of dark matter.
